ATTACK_DESCRIPTION.en: Increases the damage all your weapons do.

DEFENCE_DESCRIPTION.en: Decreases the damage you take from all attacks.

LUCK_DESCRIPTION.en: Increases the chance of getting loot and coins.

PUSH_FB_FRIEND_INSTALLS_GAME.en: Your friend %U just started playing! Go challenge them!

PUSH_FRIEND_CHALLENGED.en: Your friend %U challenged you to a new battle!

PUSH_YOUR_TURN.en: It's Bazooka time! Your turn to fight %U!

PUSH_BATTLE_EXPIRY_REMINDER_720.en: Your battle with %U will expire soon! Hurry up or the battle will be lost!

PUSH_BATTLE_EXPIRY_REMINDER_30.en: Hurry and finish your turn! You are only moments away from losing to %U!

ACCOUNT_SWITCH_DESCRIPTION.en: This person already has an account. Load account?

ACCOUNT_CREATION_FACEBOOK_HINT.en: Duel your Facebook friends. Penguins don't spam.

ACCOUNT_CREATION_NICK_TAKEN.en: Sorry, but %U is already taken. How about:

ACCOUNT_CREATION_NICK_MALFORMED.en: That's not a nice nick for a penguin, needs to be 4-20 characters long and contain only numbers and normal letters.

ACCOUNT_CREATION_ACCOUNT_CHANGED_MESSAGE.en: Hey, you logged in the game with different account than before. The game continues with the new account!

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_DEFAULT.en: Want a custom account name? Change it now.

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_CANNOT_.en: From now on you will forever be known as:

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_NICK_TA.en: Sorry, but %U is already taken. How about:

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_NICK_CH.en: Yay! Now your account has a name!

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_NICK_LE.en: A proper name for a penguin needs to be 4-20 characters long.

ACCOUNT_MODIFICATION_DESCRIPTION_NICK_IN.en: A proper name for a penguin can't have weird characters.

ERROR_200_DESCRIPTION.en: We have put our servers in the ice for a bit of regular maintenance. We'll be back in a few moments.

FORCED_UPDATE_DESCRIPTION.en: Yay! There is a new update in the App Store. Update now to the latest version.

BATTLE_LOCK_POP_UP_MESSAGE_TEXT.en: There seems to be some problems with the connection. Please try again in couple minutes.

BATTLE_SERVER_CONNECTION_FAILED_POP_UP_M.en: Cannot connect to matchmaker or battle server. Please try again.

CUSTOM_GAME_JOIN_ERROR.en: Either the game you tried to join doesn't exist or something fishy is going on. Please try again and double check the game name!

ERROR01_DESCRIPTION.en: You need to have an active internet connection to play Crazy Penguin Wars. Please enable your wi-fi and try again.

ERROR02_DESCRIPTION.en: Crazy Penguin Wars is having trouble connecting to the interwebs right now - try again?

ERROR03_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that the problem persists - reload the game to fix the problem.

ERROR04_DESCRIPTION.en: Crazy Penguin Wars has encountered a hiccup and needs to restart - Penguins are hard at work fixing this problem.

ERROR05_DESCRIPTION.en: Why not try connecting with Facebook friends instead?

ERROR06_DESCRIPTION.en: We can't retrieve Facebook info right now, please try again later. Try starting a game with a random penguin in the meantime!

ERROR07_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that penguins have been gnawing on our server cables and we need to reload the game.

ERROR08_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that this Facebook account is already associated with a player. Would you like to load their game?

ERROR09_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that your opponent's turn has taken the wrong turn. Please try loading it again later.

ERROR10_DESCRIPTION.en: This replay suggests a disturbance in the space-time continuum and therefore it has to be skipped.

ERROR11_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that your opponent's turn is hiding somewhere and we can't find it right now.  Please try again later.

ERROR12_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that your opponent's turn is nowhere to be found.  Please try again later.

ERROR13_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that the location of this battle was sucked up by a void. Please check back later while we investigate.

ERROR14_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that a battle caused our servers go BOOM. Please check back later while do some cleanup.

ERROR15_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that your opponent's turn has some issues. Please try loading it again later while we try to calm it down.

ERROR16_DESCRIPTION.en: We couldn't log you in with Facebook, please check your Facebook settings and try again.

ERROR_GENERIC_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems that your penguin caused a cuteness overdose to the game and it needs to restart.

UPSELL_WEAPONFUL_TITLE.en: Revenge is a dish best served...

UPSELL_WEAPONFUL_MESSAGE_OPPONENT_SCORE.en: Your opponent just used one and scored

RATING_SUBTITLE.en: Give us a rating and Like us

RATING_TIME.en: Rating takes less than a minute

MATCH_LOADING_ASSETS.en: Moving bits and pieces in the internet...

TOOLTIP_HOME_SCREEN_CHALLENGED.en: You've been challenged by a Mystery penguin. Play your turn now!

TOOLTIP_HOME_SCREEN_NEW_GAME.en: Time to challenge opponents.\nStart a new game now!

TOOLTIP_HOME_SCREEN_OPPONENTS_TURN_HEADE.en: Your opponent is playing right now!

TOOLTIP_HOME_SCREEN_OPPONENTS_TURN_TEXT.en: Enable notifications or pull down to refresh the list to notify you when it is your turn

DIALOG_RESTORE_PURCHASES_FAILURE_DESCRIP.en: Sorry, but your purchases have already been restored.

PRACTICE_POP_UP_MESSAGE_TEXT.en: In practice mode you can try out a few different weapons without wasting ammo. No boosters or completing challenges possible!

CUSTOM_GAME_PRACTICE_DESCRIPTION.en: In practice mode you can try out few different weapons without wasting ammo.

CUSTOM_GAME_PRIVATE_DESCRIPTION.en: Invite your friends to a private game. Remember to share the game name with them!

GAME_SETTINGS_BUTTON_CONNECT_FB_HINT.en: Helps you keep your game progress, even when playing on multiple devices.

CUSTOM_GAME_NO_GAME.en: There is no game with that name

CUSTOM_GAME_ALREADY_EXISTS.en: A game with that name already exists

HOST_LEFT_LOBBY_TEXT.en: The player that created this game has left.

TOOLTIP_CONNECT_FACEBOOK_HEADER.en: Connect now and challenge your friends.

TOOLTIP_CONNECT_FACEBOOK_DESCRIPTION.en: Don't worry, penguins don't spam fellow penguin friends.

NO_KEYBOARD_IN_FULLSCREEN.en: Keyboard is disabled when in full screen mode.

TRANSACTION_FEEDBACK_SUCCESSFUL_NO_UNLOC.en: Here is an extra %U coins bonus!

TRANSACTION_FEEDBACK_UNSUCCESSFUL_DESCRI.en: It seems that this transaction has already been processed.\nFor further assistance, please contact the AppStore customer service.
It seems that this transaction is invalid.\nFor further assistance, please contact the AppStore customer service.

TRANSACTION_FEEDBACK_FAILED_DESCRIPTION.en: We are sorry, but your transaction was not processed.\nPlease contact our customer support to seek assistance.

TRANSACTION_FEEDBACK_FAILED_HINT.en: Your transaction id has been copied to the clipboard, please paste it in your message.

PREMIUM_PURCHASE_CONFIRM_CANCELED_TITLE.en: Sorry. The transaction cannot be completed at this time. Please try again later.

PREMIUM_PURCHASE_HELP.en: For questions regarding this transaction, please contact us through our Customer Support page at http://www.digitalchocolate.com

PREMIUM_PURCHASE_TERMS.en: All purchases subject to Digital Chocolate terms of service

MENU_DESC_OUT_OF_PREMIUM.en: You need more Premium Currency to buy this.

NO_ITC_CONNECTION_HEADER.en: Cannot connect to the App Store

NO_ITC_CONNECTION_DESCRIPTION.en: It seems there is a problem connecting to the App Store.\nPlease retry or come back later.

FISH_PACKAGE_1_DESC.en: For those cold dark Antarctic winters.\nUsed to unlock weapons or exchange for coins.

FISH_PACKAGE_2_DESC.en: The day's catch.\nUsed to unlock weapons or exchange for coins.

FISH_PACKAGE_3_DESC.en: Cause swimming in fish is the new thing.\nUsed to unlock weapons or exchange for coins.

FISH_PACKAGE_4_DESC.en: That is a whole lot of fish!\nUsed to unlock weapons or exchange for coins.

FISH_PACKAGE_5_DESC.en: For the tycoons at heart.\nUsed to unlock weapons or exchange for coins.

COINS_PACKAGE1_DESC.en: Fits into a pocket, affords you an arsenal.\nUsed to buy more ammo

COINS_PACKAGE2_DESC.en: Save little now, buy lots of rockets later.\nUsed to buy more ammo.

COINS_PACKAGE3_DESC.en: That's a lot of coins for a penguin!\nUsed to buy more ammo.

COINS_PACKAGE4_DESC.en: Cause penguins know where the rainbows end.\nUsed to buy more ammo.

COINS_PACKAGE5_DESC.en: Yarr! I'm a mighty penguin\nUsed to buy more ammo.

BUNDLES_DESCRIPTION.en: Handy kits for the adventurous penguin

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_EMOTICON.en: Rockets aren't enough? You can always accompany them with an EMOTICON.

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_PLAYER_REPLAY.en: This is your last played turn, in case you need to freshen up your memory.

FIRST_TIME_FRIENDLY_MATCH.en: You can connect with Facebook and challenged your friends

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_TURN.en: Now you fight a real opponent. Use all you have learned!

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_POST_ATTACK_NOHIT.en: No worries, you'll do better next turn.

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_SUBMIT_TURN_NEW_GAME.en: You could wait for your opponent to play their turn or start a new game.

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_SUBMIT_TURN_NEXT_GAME.en: You could wait for your opponent to play their turn or move to the next game.

FIRST_TIME_FIRST_REPLAY.en: This is your opponent's turn. You can skip it, but you will miss all the action.

FIRST_TIME_SECOND_TURN.en: I think you are getting the hang of it. Remember to stock up on ammo!

FIRST_TIME_WAITING_NEW_GAME.en: You can always start a new game while you wait for your next turn.

FIRST_TIME_WAITING_NEXT_GAME.en: You can always move to the next game while you wait for your next turn.

TUTORIAL_ACTIONS_AIM_MODES.en: %s can only be dropped. Remember to take some DISTANCE before it goes boom!

TUTORIAL_ACTIONS_SCORE.en: Good job building up these points! Remember, first player to reach %U, WINS the match.

TUTORIAL_INTRO_DESCRIPTION.en: Ready to blow things up?\n\nLet's go through the basics and find out how to move around and fire rockets.

TUTORIAL_MOVE.en: Use the buttons at the bottom to move LEFT and RIGHT. Go for that ammo supplies crate.

TUTORIAL_SHOOT.en: Go ahead, DRAG the AIM button OUT to direct your bazooka.

TUTORIAL_END_TURN.en: No more actions this TURN. Use the checkmark button to END your TURN.

TUTORIAL_OPPONENTS_TURN.en: It is now your opponent's TURN. Wait for it to end.

TUTORIAL_TACTICAL_MOVES.en: You can JUMP, by DRAGGING the SPRING down.

TUTORIAL_JUMP.en: Go ahead, try JUMPING over there.

TUTORIAL_CHANGE_WEAPON.en: Change your weapon by tapping the WEAPON button.

TUTORIAL_SELECT_WEAPON.en: TAP the PISTOL to select it.

TUTORIAL_EQUIP_WEAPON.en: EQUIP it by tapping the EQUIP BUTTON.

TUTORIAL_CLOSE_SHOP.en: Now CLOSE the window and get ready to shoot!

TUTORIAL_ATTACK_AP.en: Remember, you can only shoot ONCE every turn, so make the most of it!

TUTORIAL_POINTS.en: The first player to reach %U POINTS wins!

TUTORIAL_COVER.en: Good cover is crucial. Try getting there.

TUTORIAL_MOVE_AP.en: Moving takes ENERGY. Keep an eye on the ENERGY dial.

TUTORIAL_JUMP_AP.en: Jumping takes a lot of ENERGY, so make sure you have enough before you JUMP.

TUTORIAL_BRING_IT_ON.en: Great cover! Now END your TURN.

TUTORIAL_PREMIUM_WEAPON.en: Time for some big explosions. Try out the MINI-BAZOOKA!

TUTORIAL_SELECT_PREMIUM_WEAPON.en: TAP the MINI-BAZOOKA to select it.

TUTORIAL_PREMIUM_WEAPON_AMMO.en: GREAT! Now all you need is some AMMO.

TUTORIAL_CLOSE_SHOP_PREMIUM.en: Now get ready for some serious rocket action!

TUTORIAL_PREMIUM_WEAPON_UNLOCK.en: Use your Emerald FISH to UNLOCK the MINI-BAZOOKA!

TUTORIAL_FIRE_PREMIUM_WEAPON.en: Try getting a SAFE DISTANCE away before shooting this.

TUTORIAL_WINNING.en: Nice work!\nRemember, the first player that reaches %U POINTS wins!

TUTORIAL_MATCH_WON.en: I’ve never seen a penguin as skilled with a bazooka as you! I think you're ready!

TUTORIAL_POINTS_SCORED.en: Great! Only %U more points to win!

TUTORIAL_NO_POINTS_SCORED.en: Try AIMING a bit better next time, remember to calibrate your aiming over obstacles.

TUTORIAL_SHOP_GENERIC.en: Always remember to keep your AMMO stock high.

TUTORIAL_SHOP_AMMO_PURCHASE.en: AMMO is great, more AMMO is even greater!

VIP_MEMBERSHIP_SUBSCRIPTION_INACTIVE.en: Buy time from below to activate the benefits.

VERY_FEW_COINS_POP_UP_MESSAGE.en: You can always trade some fish for coins. Would you like to exchange some now?

QUEUE_WAITING_MESSAGE.en: We are matching you with a random opponent.\nOnce they play their turn we'll notify you ASAP.

QUEUE_STILL_WAITING_MESSAGE.en: You are already in the queue.\nWe will hook you up with an opponent ASAP.

SURRENDER_CONFIRMATION_MESSAGE.en: There are no rewards for quitters.

EXIT_BATTLE_CONFIRMATION_MESSAGE.en: This will end your turn. Are you sure?

UNUSED_ACTIONS_TITLE.en: Are you sure you want to end your turn?

UNUSED_ACTIONS_MESSAGE.en: You haven't used your attacks action yet!

LEVEL_UP_DESC.en: You have reached a new level!\nHere is your reward:

DROP_OUT_OF_MATCH_MESSAGE.en: You have been dropped from the match, but you still get to keep everything you collected before disconnecting.

NOT_ENOUGH_COINS_POP_UP_TUTORIAL_MESSAGE.en: You don't have enough coins for this! Come back later when you earn some.

NOT_ENOUGH_COINS_POP_UP_MESSAGE.en: You're out of coins! Would you like to buy some more?

NOT_ENOUGH_CASH_POP_UP_MESSAGE.en: You're out of fish! Would you like to buy some more?

MORE_BATTLES_POP_UP_MESSAGE.en: You have more battles, load next battle?

TOOLTIP_TOO_MANY_GAMES_DESCRIPTION.en: Please delete some old games before creating new ones.

FIND_GAME_FEEDBACK_YOUR_OWN_NICK.en: We are sorry, we can't clone penguins....yet!

FIND_GAME_FEEDBACK_INVALID_NICK.en: That penguin name has some weird characters.

FIND_GAME_FEEDBACK_NOTFOUND.en: This name does not exist in the penguin archives.

FIND_GAME_FEEDBACK_PLAYER_ADDED.en: %U is now added to your friends!

FIND_GAME_SUBHEADER.en: Choose a way to find an opponent

LEVELUP_DESCRIPTION.en: Well done! You reached level %U! You unlocked new weapons!

EASTEREGGDESC.en: Use these festive rubber chicken eggs to spread explosive fun.

CANNONDESC.en: Unleash delicious chocolate destruction on the battlefield.

FB_OPEN_GRAPH_LEVEL_DESC.en: I just gained a level! That means I'm better than you. Wanna fight about it?

FB_OPEN_GRAPH_WEAPON_DESC.en: Let me demonstrate it on you, hold still.

FB_OPEN_GRAPH_DUEL_DESC.en: You have no chance to defeat me. I dare you to challenge me!

TIP_HOW_TO_EARN.en: Play and Win matches to earn coins.

TIP_HOW_TO_GET_WEAPONS.en: Earn coins and buy more ammo from the shop.

TIP_HOW_TO_WIN.en: First to collect %s points in a match wins.

TIP_HOW_TO_GET_XP.en: The points you earn from playing matches are turned into XP and coins.

TIP_HOW_TO_LEVEL_UP.en: You level up when you earn XP in your matches.

TIP_HOW_TO_EARN_PC.en: You earn precious & delicious fish every time you level up.

TIP_GAMECENTER.en: Connect with Game Center and challenge friends!

TIP_FACEBOOK.en: Use Facebook to play with your friends!

TIP_GRENADE.en: You do not need to remove the safety pin from the grenade!

TIP_HOW_TO_USE_ACTIONPOINTS.en: You can always move your penguin as long as you have energy, even after you attack.

TIP_HOW_TO_SEND_TURN.en: Send your turn and wait for the opponent to play!

TIP_RAN_OUT_OF_COINS.en: Ran out of coins? No worries, you can always exchange fish for coins at the Shop.

TIP_JUMPING_ACTION_POINTS.en: Jumping is fun, but it consumes energy.

TIP_HOW_TO_DESTROY_OBJECTS.en: You can destroy objects that are made of ice, wood or stone and get XP.

TIP_DO_NOT_FALL_DOWN.en: Do not fall down from the cliff!

TIP_BATTLE_RANDOM_OPPONENTS.en: You can battle against random opponents.

TIP_KILLING BONUS.en: You get a bonus if you kill your opponent

TIP_MANY MATCHES_ONGOING.en: You can have as many matches active at the same time as you want!

TIP_MATCHES_EXPIRE.en: Matches expire in %s days, be sure to  play before that.

TIP_NO_SWIMMING.en: These penguins can't swim, so avoid the water.

ACHIEVEMENTS_ACCEPT_REMATCH_DESCRIPTION.en: Get challenged for a rematch %u times.

ACHIEVEMENTS_WINBAZOOKA_DESCRIPTION.en: Win %u games using only the Bazooka.

ACHIEVEMENTS_WINIMPACTCANNON_DESCRIPTION.en: Win %u games using only the Impact Cannon.

ACHIEVEMENTS_KILLDCHOC_DESCRIPTION.en: For winning over a Crazy Penguin Wars: Tiny Duels developer.

ACHIEVEMENTS_KILLSMATCH_DESCRIPTION.en: For killing 3 times in a row in one match.

ARMORPIERCINGROCKETDESC.en: Use it to shoot through objects but not through terrain.

BASICNUKEDESC.en: Deals small damage in a small area

BEANBAGDESC.en: Has a powerful knockback. Use it to push people and objects.

CLUSTERGRENADEDESC.en: Grenade that splits into smaller explosives. Useful on groups of enemies that are in cover.

CLUSTERROCKETDESC.en: Missile that splits into smaller rockets. Takes a second to deploy after firing.

DOOMSDAYDEVICEDESC.en: The ultimate weapon that can easily destroy a whole map. Very hard to avoid.

DRILLDESC.en: When thrown on the ground the drillbot digs a tunnel straight down.

DYNAMITEDESC.en: Dynamite drops at your feet and it has 4 second timer.

FLAMETHROWERDESC.en: Sprays a short range jet of fire. Be careful not to set yourself on fire as the flames tend to bounce easily.

FRAGMENTATIONMISSILEDESC.en: Missile that leaves sharp fragments on the ground.

GASGRENADEDESC.en: Bounces around and it has a 3 second timer. The gas damages everyone that comes in contact.

GRENADEDESC.en: Bounces around and has a 4 second timer. Useful on enemies that are in cover.

GREYGOODESC.en: The ultimate in nanotechnology. Guaranteed to destroy everything forever!

HEATSEEKERDESC.en: Doesn't actually target heat sources, but has an affinity for penguins.

LEMONGRENADEDESC.en: Grenade that explodes into a spray of acid. Burns through terrain and does damage over time.

MEGANUKEDESC.en: Deals massive damage in a large area

MINIGUNDESC.en: Shoots multiple bullets in a relatively straight line.

MOLOTOVDESC.en: Shatters against surfaces to spread flames.

MORTARDESC.en: Works the same as bazooka but has greatly improved range.

ORBITALLASERDESC.en: Target with the mouse pointer to call down a powerful blast from space. Make sure the path is clear.

PISTOLDESC.en: Shoots a bullet in a relatively straight line.

PLASMACANNONDESC.en: Shoots with a slight arc and is more effective the more accurate the shot.

POINTTELEPORTDESC.en: Use mouse to point the teleporter. Teleporting causes small damage and knockback effect on nearby enemies and teleports you to the desired location.

PUNCHDESC.en: Use to punch your enemies off cliffs.

RAILGUNDESC.en: Use it to shoot through terrain and obstacles.

ROCKDESC.en: The heavy rock is useful for pushing people and for collapsing structures.

SHOTGUNDESC.en: Deals more damage depending on how close you are to opponents.

STICKYBOMBDESC.en: Bomb that explodes into sticky glue. Prevents jumping and slows movement.

TELEPORTATIONGRENADEDESC.en: Works the same as grenade with 3 second timer. Deals small damage and knockback effect to nearby enemies and teleports you where it lands.

VOIDGENERATORDESC.en: Destroys massive amount of terrain and sucks in objects and players.

MINIBAZOOKADESC.en: Shoots a series of small missiles. Useful against groups of enemies or for collapsing structures.

NAPALMDESC.en: Napalm Canister drops at your feet and has a 3 second timer.

SNIPERRIFLEDESC.en: Long range projectile weapon that can fire through multiple enemies.

CINDERGRENADEDESC.en: Grenade that drops flames as it travels. Explodes after 4 seconds and will ignite opponents.

IMPACTCANNONDESC.en: Extremely close range weapon with huge knockback to both you and the opponent.

SHIELDWALLDESC.en: Blocks weapons from passing through it.

FLAREGUNDESC.en: Shoots a burning bullet in a slight arc. The bullet bounces around and can ignite enemies.

LASERPISTOLDESC.en: Effective against penguins, balloons and body hair.

PLASMAMORTARDESC.en: Unloads unspeakable plasmatic horror at a desired location.

FIREHOSEDESC.en: Disperses protesters and puts out fires, or both at the same time!

MININGLASERDESC.en: Instantly digs massive tunnels in any direction. Though it doesn't really harm penguins.

PLASMABOMBDESC.en: Unleash the awesome power of plasma with a controlled charge.

GRENADELAUNCHERDESC.en: Fires grenades faster than you could hope to throw them.

FUELAIRBOMBDESC.en: Detonates in the air and unleashes a rain of fire.

ARTILLERYSTRIKEDESC.en: Call in artillery support by placing this marker beacon.

WATERBALLOONDESC.en: It doesn't hurt much, but penguins don't like getting wet.

WANDWINDDESC.en: Shoots a slow moving tornado that pushes around enemies and objects. Ignores terrain.

FIREWORKSDESC.en: A short range rocket that creates a series of explosions.

CATDESC.en: Requires precise aim and causes enemies to be knocked around by an enraged feline.
